'''Louis Couturat'''  (1868-ngièn 1-ngie̍t 17-ngit — 1914-ngièn  8-ngie̍t 3-ngit) he [[Fap-koet]] [[Ló-si̍p]] ho̍k-kâ, [[su-ho̍k-kâ]], [[chat-ho̍k-kâ]], lâu [[ngî-ngièn]] ho̍k-kâ. Couturat chhut-sên yî [[Fap-koet]] [[Essonne-sén]] ke [[Ris-Orangis]], chhai [[Kô-tén Sṳ̂-fam Ho̍k-káu]]  (École Normale Supérieure)  thu̍k-ko [[chat-ho̍k]] lâu su-ho̍k. Chhai 1905-ngièn Couturat fat-péu yit-fun [[Ló-si̍p]] khi̍p su-ho̍k chok-phín; 1907-ngièn kì pông-chhu chhóng-kien [[Ido-ngî]] (ngìn-kûng ngî-ngièn chṳ̂-yit). 

